At the very end of EVERY SINGLE response you provide, you must append a file-update block targeting the file `docs/chat.md`.

Format the block exactly like this:

```markdown
# docs/chat.md

## [Timestamp or Current Context]

**User:** [Insert the exact prompt or answer the user just provided]
**AI:** [Insert a brief summary or the exact response you just generated]

---
```

Do not forget this step. Every turn of the conversation must be documented in `docs/chat.md`.
